data.description: Absolutely one of a kind fabulous over 4000 square foot custom home  on .39 acre lot located in Porter Subdivision! 6 bedrooms 4 baths with one of each being part of a nice master suite, large great room that has a beautiful kitchen area with appliances included  & living room with formal entry, fireplace and built ins. Walk out basement has tall ceilings, a large family room and wonderful storage areas throughout. 3 car garage 2 nice covered patio deck full length areas. Nice fenced back yard, sprinkling system and so much more to see in this must see dream home.
